<%- include("partials/header") -%>

<section id="hero" class="bg-light py-5">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="text-center">Why does this website exist?</h2>
    <p class="text-center">
      Most importantly, to make me a better thinker. The process of writing, I
      believe, is a sort of learning because it makes you give a structure to
      what you already know and further develop your thoughts. Plus, itâ€™s fun!
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="about" class="py-5">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <p>
      Just like you, I am a human being. One of my biggest concerns is to get
      the most out of my time, so I love doing things that will help me become
      better - mostly those I'm curious about.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="blog" class="bg-light py-5">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Blog</h2>
    <div class="row">
      <% for (let post of posts) { %>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title"><%= post.title %></h3>
            <p class="card-text"><%= post.body.substring(0,100)%> ...</p>
            <a href="/posts/<%=post.title%>" class="btn btn-primary"
              >Read More</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

